                                    <justification>getNextBatch(int) replaced by getNextBatch(int, DynamicFilterSnapshot) returning List — dynamic filter predicate is now delivered per-batch and ConnectorSplitBatch wrapper removed</justification>
                                </item>
                                <item>
                                    <code>java.method.numberOfParametersChanged</code>
